## ðŸ’• About the Series
*Crash Landing on You* tells the story of **Yoon Se-ri**, a South Korean heiress who accidentally crash-lands in **North Korea**. There, she meets **Ri Jeong-hyeok**, a kind-hearted North Korean officer who helps her find her way home.

> "Even if I were born again, I will still find you, and I will still love you."
